// Responsive Breakpoints
- Breakpoints:
  * Desktop: > 1200px
  * Tablet: 768px - 1199px
  * Mobile: < 767px

// Mobile Header
- Mobile Navigation:
  * Hamburger Menu
  * Logo (centered)
  * Quick Actions:
    - Language Toggle
    - Login Button
  * Slide-out Menu:
    - Ana Menü
    - Alt Menüler
    - İletişim Bilgileri

// Mobile Dashboard
- Stack Layout:
  * Full Width Cards
  * Scrollable Tables
  * Simplified Charts
  * Touch-friendly Buttons:
    - Min height: 44px
    - Min width: 44px
    - Padding: 12px

// Mobile Forms
- Form Elements:
  * Large Input Fields
    - Height: 48px
    - Font-size: 16px
  * Touch-friendly Dropdowns
  * Native Date Pickers
  * Full Width Buttons

// Tablet Adaptations
- Two Column Layout:
  * Sidebar (collapsible)
  * Main Content
  * Flexible Grids:
    - 2 columns on tablet
    - 1 column on mobile

// Touch Interactions
- Gesture Support:
  * Swipe Actions:
    - Menu Navigation
    - Table Scroll
    - Gallery Navigation
  * Pinch to Zoom:
    - Images
    - Documents
  * Pull to Refresh:
    - Lists
    - Dashboards 